結左婚我唔知<br />\n我老母就話唔係自己堂妹都唔認得呀<br />\n我望多佢兩眼<br />\n又真係有幾分相似<br />\n幾年冇見靚左咁多<br />\n由其係對眼<br />\n真係女大十八變<br />\n望到我有小小心動<br />\n咁我老母又叫我坐佢隔離<br />\n話咩我畢業冇耐<br />\n佢又入左大學同佢傾下計<br />\n咁咪照坐吹下水應酬下<br />\n點知又幾好傾<br />\n中間有幾下同佢對望係度諗<br />\n如果有個咁既女朋友就好<br />\n又靚又傾得埋<br />\n呢個諗法真係不得了<br />\n因為我知道我地係冇可能<br />\n但呢幾日個腦入面都係佢個樣<br />\n訓覺前又係諗起佢<br />\n我諗我真係鍾意左佢<br />\n點算"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:43:14.000Z","msg":"試過個表妹同我表白 不過嗰陣有鍾意嘅人所以拒絕咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d18b388adb50dc39fbb36911fc1e5fdd6c51db","tid":1025872,"uid":199265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:07:06.000Z","msg":"首先佢要鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b0485c18b7f6bb5283170d88da80ba2197e013","tid":1025872,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef4db3d9d5ee6e0da89a8ddf068d567f34cfc828","tid":1025872,"uid":34828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap181&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxmjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=cceafbb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap181</a><br />\n<br />\n附表5"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"揾唔到邊句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb86eb189959300a9574ab0e2d2a9161b0cb72ed","tid":1025872,"uid":53361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca752a1f779f91ddd4b8ede3bdfe49254ee246d","tid":1025872,"uid":44646,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"25423f552eb766aeb4e88f22e2cd947624ae1abd","tid":1025872,"uid":53361,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"8a0b5168133ce73bd992612f54d4eb2fc5c84d74","tid":1025872,"uid":13804,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy"